Changelog For Users
------------------_
Last Changed: $Revision$ $Date$

Revision: 2499 Date: 2006-07-20 14:39:03 +0200 (Thu, 20 Jul 2006)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
*	Changed Database structure on tbl_users
		create_timestamp converted from integer to timestamp
		last_timestamp converted from integer to timestamp

Revision: 2497 Date: 2006-07-20 14:18:29 +0200 (Thu, 20 Jul 2006)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
*	Added Users::updateLastTimestamp($timestamp=null)
		This allows to set last_timestamp
		
*	Added DAO_User::updateLastTimestamp($id, $timestamp)
		This allow to set last_timestamp, see also 
		Users::updateLastTimestamp
		
* 	Added MySQLi_User::updateLastTimestamp($id, $timestamp)
		This allow to set last_timestamp, see also 
		Users::updateLastTimestamp

		
Revision: 2096 Date: 2006-05-31 16:25:35 +0200 (Wed, 31 May 2006)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
*	Added UsersDecorator::getUsername()

*	Changed UsersDecorator::getUID()
		this function is not abstract any more, instead a simple
		implementation of getUID() have been implemented

*	ChangeLog Started